'''Multycorp''' was one of the largest corporations on [[Vorzyd IV]] before and around the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Its corporate building had at least twenty-four floors with assembly on floors seven and eight, manufacturing on floors nine and ten, accounting on floor twenty-four and the central computer in the basement.

